      "amount": "2 tbsp"
    },
    {
      "name": "lemon zest",
      "amount": "1 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and minced garlic and sauté until onions are translucent.",
    "Stir in minced beef, breaking it apart, and cook until browned.",
    "Add diced bell pepper and tomatoes, cooking until softened.",
    "Season with paprika, salt, and black pepper, stirring well.",
    "Pour in water and add saffron threads, bringing the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add short grain rice, stir to coat the grains with the sauce, and reduce heat to low.",
    "Cover the skillet and let it simmer for 20 minutes until the rice is tender and liquid is absorbed.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley and lemon zest before serving."
  ],
